/*EXI *  TEXT('Midas PB Portfolio Instrument Types list')
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  Midas - Private Banking Module                               *
      *                                                               *
      *  PB0230 - Midas PB Portfolio Instrument Types list            *
      *                                                               *
      *  Function:  This program print all records contained in       *
      *             LF/SDPLINL0 .                                     *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: PBC0230 - Instrument Types List                   *
      *                                                               *
      *  (c) Finastra International Limited 2001                      *
      *                                                               *
